  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0db4\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One person was killed by a stampede at the gas station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person who was pushed in the queue during a rush at the Matugama Pelawatta petrol station has died after falling ill and being admitted to the hospital, according to Meghathanna police.",
        "P., a resident of Valallavita Avitta, has died. that. The police say that he is a 65-year-old man named Gunasiri",
        "When the man fell down unconscious while queuing for fuel in the queue due to the heavy traffic, the local residents of the place were taken to Meghathanna hospital by car.",
        "The police say that this person has died there. In this petrol station, the system prescribed by the government was not implemented, and before this, there were many irregularities, the residents said.",
        "In the last two days, long queues were seen near the Pelawatta petrol station and due to non-adherence to the recommended procedure and giving fuel in cans, many people lost fuel from the queue and were inconvenient."
      ],
